_aChangeLog.text: Changed the light of the sun on the map
Added lamps and light from them in the helicopter
Added new pipes in the helicopter
When you enter the map, an inscription about the map appeared, etc.
When you enter, you will see a beautiful angle of the helicopter
Many big and small bugs have been fixed

_aLatestUpdates._sTitle: First and last version of the map

_sText:
Find out which one of you is the best sniper on the map!
On the map you can play 1 on 1 and 2 on 2.

If you notice a map flaw or want to suggest an idea, write to the creator of the card in discord.
I will be glad to everyone :-D
Discord: lizer001#0

If you downloaded the 1.0 version of the map, then download the map again, but version 1.1!
A lot of things have been fixed in the new version of the map!
